KEAGAN Dolly bid his Mamelodi Sundowns teammates and the technical
team goodbye yesterday as he prepared to fly off to Europe to start his
international career in France.Dolly
confirmed the news to SunSport: “The deal went
well and I am happy Sundowns finally agreed to the move. It has been my dream
to play in Europe and I am glad it’s now a reality.”The
